wikipedia_page.main: Taylor Joshua McKenzie (born 30 May 1994) is an English professional footballer who plays as a defender for Enfield Town.McKenzie made his Notts County debut on 9 November 2014 in a 0–0 draw against Accrington Stanley at Meadow Lane, in the first round of the FA Cup, coming on as a 37th-minute substitute for Hayden Mullins.A few days later on 15 November 2014, he made his Football League debut against Coventry City at the Ricoh Arena in a 1–0 League One win.
